{"id":"docs","title":"Introduction to the Angular docs","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/marketing/docs.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"introduction-to-the-angular-docs\" translation-result=\"on\">Angular 文件簡介<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"docs#introduction-to-the-angular-docs\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 class=\"no-toc\" translation-origin=\"off\">Introduction to the Angular docs<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"docs#introduction-to-the-angular-docs\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Angular 是一個應用設計框架與開發平台，旨在建立高效而精緻的單頁面應用。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Angular is an application-design framework and development platform for creating efficient and sophisticated single-page apps.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">這份 Angular 文件會幫助你學習和使用 Angular 框架與開發平台，從你的第一個應用開始，一直到最佳化複雜的企業級單頁面應用。\n這些課程和指南中都包含可下載的範例，以加速你的學習。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">These Angular docs help you learn and use the Angular framework and development platform, from your first application to optimizing complex single-page applications for enterprises.\nTutorials and guides include downloadable examples to help you start your projects.</p>\n\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n  <a href=\"tutorial/first-app\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Work through a full tutorial\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">建構你的第一個 Angular 應用</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Build your first Angular app</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">完成一個完整的課程，建立你的第一個應用程式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Work through a full tutorial to create your first application.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">應用課程</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Homes App Tutorial</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/what-is-angular\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular Platform Overview\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">什麼是 Angular</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">What is Angular</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">對 Angular 平台進行一次高層概覽。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Get a high-level overview of the Angular platform.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">平台概覽</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Platform overview</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/architecture\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular Concepts\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">深入探索</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Learn and Explore</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">學習 Angular 應用的更多知識及架構特性</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn about the fundamental design concepts and architecture of Angular applications.</p>\n      \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">架構</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Introduction to Angular concepts</p>\n      \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/setup-local\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Angular Local Environment Setup\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">搭建環境</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Set up your environment</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">使用 Angular CLI 搭建本地開發環境。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Set up your local environment for development with the Angular CLI.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">本地搭建</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Local setup</p>\n    \n  </a>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"assumptions\" translation-result=\"on\">基本假設<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"docs#assumptions\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Assumptions<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"docs#assumptions\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">本文件假設你已經熟悉了 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML\" title=\"Learn HTML\">HTML</a>，<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Learn/CSS/First_steps\" title=\"Learn CSS\">CSS</a>，<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/A_re-introduction_to_JavaScript\" title=\"Learn JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> 和來自 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Language_Resources\" title=\"Latest JavaScript standards\">最新標準</a> 的一些知識，比如  <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Classes\" title=\"ES2015 Classes\">類</a> 和 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/import\" title=\"ES2015 Modules\">模組</a>。\n下列程式碼範例都是用最新版本的 <a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/\" title=\"TypeScript\">TypeScript</a> 寫的。\n大多數 Angular 程式碼都只能用最新的 JavaScript 編寫，它會用 <a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/classes.html\" title=\"TypeScript Types\">型別</a> 實現依賴注入，還會用<a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/decorators.html\" title=\"Decorators\">裝飾器</a>來提供元資料。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">These docs assume that you are already familiar with <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML\" title=\"Learn HTML\">HTML</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Learn/CSS/First_steps\" title=\"Learn CSS\">CSS</a>, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/A_re-introduction_to_JavaScript\" title=\"Learn JavaScript\">JavaScript</a>,\nand some of the tools from the <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Language_Resources\" title=\"Latest JavaScript standards\">latest standards</a>, such as <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Classes\" title=\"ES2015 Classes\">classes</a> and <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/import\" title=\"ES2015 Modules\">modules</a>.\nThe code samples are written using <a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/\" title=\"TypeScript\">TypeScript</a>.\nMost Angular code can be written with just the latest JavaScript, using <a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/classes.html\" title=\"TypeScript Types\">types</a> for dependency injection, and using <a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/decorators.html\" title=\"Decorators\">decorators</a> for metadata.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"私有化部署本文件譯者\">私有化部署本文件（譯者）<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"docs#私有化部署本文件譯者\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p>有些企業內部的防火牆比較嚴格，如果無法開啟 <a href=\"https://angular.cn\">https://angular.cn</a>，你可以在企業內部進行私有化部署。步驟如下：</p>\n<p>本文件的預編譯版本位於 <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/latest.angular.live\">Github</a> 上，如果你想進行私有化部署，請把它 Clone 下來，在 nginx 等伺服器上按照靜態網站的形式做部署即可，除此之外不需要任何伺服器端環境。</p>\n<p>以 Nginx 為例，你需要在 nginx 上做如下改動：</p>\n<code-example>\nserver {\n    root /path/to/ng-docs.github.io/;\n    location / {\n        try_files $uri $uri.html $uri/ /index.html;\n    }\n}\n</code-example>\n<p>注意其中的 <code>$uri.html</code>，這是本文件相對於常規 Angular 應用的主要差別，因為本文件進行了預先渲染（Prerender），這項工作可以讓你在不需要 Node 伺服器的情況下獲得等同於伺服器端渲染的體驗改善。</p>\n<h2 id=\"feedback\" translation-result=\"on\">反饋<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"docs#feedback\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Feedback<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"docs#feedback\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<!-- vale Angular.Google_We = NO -->\n<h3 id=\"你也可以和我們一起做貢獻\">你也可以和我們一起做貢獻！<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"docs#你也可以和我們一起做貢獻\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">我們希望聽到你的聲音！<a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/new/choose\" title=\"Angular GitHub repository new issue form\">歡迎報告問題或為文件的未來提交建議</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">We want to hear from you. <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/new/choose\" title=\"Angular GitHub repository new issue form\">Report problems or submit suggestions for future docs</a>.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">請到 GitHub 上的儲存庫中建立 <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/pulls\" title=\"Angular Github pull requests\">Pull Requests</a> 來為 Angular 文件做出貢獻。\n<a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md\" title=\"貢獻者指南\">貢獻者指南</a>將會幫助你更好的為社群做貢獻。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Contribute to Angular docs by creating\n<a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/pulls\" title=\"Angular Github pull requests\">pull requests</a>\non the Angular GitHub repository.\nSee <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md\" title=\"Contributing guide\">Contributing to Angular</a>\nfor information about submission guidelines.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">我們的社群提倡相互尊重、相互支援。\n參閱<a href=\"https://github.com/angular/code-of-conduct/blob/main/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md\" title=\"contributor code of conduct\">社群行為規範</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Our community values respectful, supportive communication.\nPlease consult and adhere to the <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/code-of-conduct/blob/main/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md\" title=\"Contributor code of conduct\">Code of Conduct</a>.</p>\n\n<!-- vale Angular.Google_We = YES -->\n\n  \n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/docs-style-guide\n - guide/example-apps-list\n - guide/localizing-angular\n - guide/updating\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - docs#angular-文件簡介\n - docs#assumptions\n - docs#feedback\n - docs#introduction-to-the-angular-docs\n - docs#你也可以和我們一起做貢獻\n - docs#反饋\n - docs#基本假設\n - docs#私有化部署本文件譯者\n - guide/architecture\n - guide/setup-local\n - guide/what-is-angular\n - tutorial/first-app\n - https://angular.cn\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Learn/CSS/First_steps\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/A_re-introduction_to_JavaScript\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Language_Resources\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Classes\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/import\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/new/choose\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/pulls\n - https://github.com/angular/code-of-conduct/blob/main/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/marketing/docs.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/latest.angular.live\n - https://www.typescriptlang.org/\n - https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/classes.html\n - https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/decorators.html\n-->"}